'''Taswast''' neɣ '''Tafada''' d allal n usiden n [[akud|wakud]] i wsiden n [[azemz|yizmaz]] d [[Ass|wussan]] d usuddes-nsen i yimesɣuṛa imettiyen, [[ajjed|imesɣanen]], ideblanen yakk d imsenziyen, anecta yettili-d s isebdaden yemgaraden deg [[umuɣ n teswasin|teswasin yemgaraden]], deg yakk taswasin-nni ttunefken kra n yismawen i kra n talliyin n uzemz anda tikwal ttilin d ussan neɣ d [[imalas]] neɣ d [[ayyur (akud)|ayyuren]] neɣ d [[aseggas|iseggasen]], dɣa deg waṭas n tikkal ttilin d ayyuren yakk d iseggasen i teddun yakk d tuzzya n [[Tafukt|tfukt]] deg igenni yakk d wansa n [[tagnit|tegnit]] deg [[timezzit|tmezzit-is]] ɣef tfukt, neɣ teddun yakk d tlallit d taggara n [[ayyur|wayyur]] akken daɣen illant teswasin yettganin ɣef tuzya n wayyur d tfukt d isin. Maca mači d isefki ad ggunint yakk ɣef wayyur d tfukt acku llant kra n teswasin yeggunin ɣef [[itrikli|yimtiwgen]] niden<br/>
Aṭas n [[taɣeṛma|tɣeṛmawin]] d yiɣerfen gan-d tiswasin amedya ɣer yimaziɣen ([[taswast tamaziɣt]]) 

